\id 1JN
\h 1 Yuḥanna 
\toc1 1 Yuḥanna 
\toc2 1 Yuḥanna 
\toc3 1 Yḥ. 
\mt1 1 Yuḥanna  
\c 1
\s1 Awař n Tudart  
\m
\v 1 Wenni tuɣa din zeg umezwaru, d Netta i d awem nettbarreḥ: Wenni nesřa d Wenni neẓra s tiṭṭawin nneɣ, d Wenni netwařa u nḥada t s ifassen nneɣ d Wenni iǧan d Awař Iddaren. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Lk. 24:39; Yḥ. 20:27; Yḥ. 1:1, 14; Řex. 13:26; 2 Bṭ. 1:16. \x*  
\v 2 Aqa Tudart teḍhar-dd, neccin neẓra i-tt, uca ncehhed u nettbarreḥ awem Tudart ittduman, tenni tuɣa ak-d Babatneɣ uca tᵉttwassargeb-dd i neccin.  
\v 3 Min neẓra d min nesřa, ad awem t-i-dd-nesscen, ḥima ɛawed kenniw ad tiřim deg umuni akidneɣ, uca amuni nneɣ ak-d Babatneɣ u ak-d Mmis Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 4 Aqa nettari man aya i kenniw, ḥima řefraḥet nneɣ ad tiři tekmeř.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arebbi d Tafawt  
\m
\v 5 D wa d Řexbar Aṣebḥan i zzayes nesřa uca ad awem nbarreḥ: AREBBI d Tafawt, Netta war dayes bu jjurret n taǧest. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Yḥ. 1:9; 8:12; 9:5; 12:35, 36. \x*  
\v 6 Mařa neqqar, aqa ɣarneɣ amuni akides, uca neggur di taǧest, aqa nessxarriq, war nḍeffar ca tidett.  
\v 7 Maca mařa nuyur di Tfawt, am Netta di Tfawt, ɣarneɣ amuni ak-d wayawya, uca ad taf Idammen n Yasuɛ, Mmis, ad aneɣ ssizdegen zi marra ddnub nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Ɛbr. 9:14; 1 Bṭ. 1:19; Asa. 1:5. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Mařa neqqar, war dayneɣ bu ddnub, aqa nessxarriq x yixef nneɣ uca tidett war dayneɣ teǧi. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt 1 Ij. 8:46; 2 Im. 6:36; Ayub 9:2; Izhd. 143:2; Awřn. 20:9; Amb. 7:20. \x*  
\v 9 Maca mařa nenɛem s ddnub nneɣ, aqa Netta d amtiqqi d amseggad ḥima ad aneɣ iɣfar ddnub nneɣ uca ad aneɣ issizdeg zi marra min war iseggden. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Izhd. 32:5; Awřn. 28:13. \x*  
\v 10 Mařa neqqar: ‘Neccin war dayneɣ bu ddnub!’, nettarra i-t d bu-ixarriqen uca awař nnes war dayneɣ iǧi.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Uyurem di Tfawt  
\m
\v 1 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* iḥenjiren inu\bd*, uriɣ aya i kenniw, ḥima war txeṭṭim ca. Uca mařa ixḍa ca n ijjen, aqa ɣarneɣ Umseṣřaḥ, d Wenni iǧan ɣar Babatneɣ, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, Amseggad. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Tim. 2:5; Ɛbr. 7:25. \x*  
\v 2 Maɣar Netta d aṣřaḥ i ddnub nneɣ, war iǧi x ddnub nneɣ waha, maca ɛawed i yinni n ddunect marra. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Yḥ. 4:42; Rum. 3:25; 2 Kur. 5:18; Kul. 1:20; 1 Yḥ. 4:10, 14. \x*   
\m
\v 3 S man aya i nettwařa belli aqa nessen i-t, mařa neṭṭef di tweṣṣa nnes.  
\v 4 Wenni iqqaren: “Necc ssneɣ t!”, maca war iṭṭif ca di tweṣṣa nnes, netta d bu-ixarriqen uca tidett war dayes teǧi. \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Yḥ. 4:20. \x*  
\v 5 Maca wenni ittᵉṭṭfen deg wawař nnes, ad dayes tkemmeř tayri n AREBBI s tidett. S man aya nessen, belli aqa neccin dayes. \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Yḥ. 13:35. \x*  
\v 6 Wenni iqqaren: ‘Necc dayes!’, ittxeṣṣa ad yuyur am mammec tuɣa iggur Netta. \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Yḥ. 13:15; 1 Bṭ. 2:21. \x*   
\m
\v 7 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* imɛizzen inu\bd*, war d awem ttariɣ ca tawṣeyyet n jdid, maca tawṣeyyet taqdimt i tuɣa ɣarwem zeg umezwaru. Tawṣeyyet-a taqdimt d awař i tuɣa tesřim. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Yḥ. 3:23; 2 Yḥ. 5. \x*  
\v 8 Waxxa amenni ad awem dd-ariɣ tawṣeyyet n jdid, tenni iǧan d tidett dayes u daywem, minzi taǧest teɛdu uca Tafawt n tidett aqa tᵉtteḍhar-dd řexxu. \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Yḥ. 13:34; 15:12. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Wenni iqqaren belli aqa-t di Tfawt, \add maca\add* icarreh umas, netta aqa-t di taǧest ař iḍa.  
\v 10 Wenni ittexsen umas, ad iqqim di Tfawt uca war dayes bu řefḍiḥet i zi ɣa inqard \add umas\add*. \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Yḥ. 12:35; 1 Yḥ. 3:14. \x*  
\v 11 Maca wenni icarrhen umas, aqa-t di taǧest uca iggur di taǧest, war issin mani ɣa iraḥ, minzi taǧest tessdarɣeř tiṭṭawin nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tayri n Arebbi, Babatneɣ  
\m
\v 12 Ad awem dd-ariɣ, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* iḥenjiren\bd*, minzi ddnub nwem ttwaɣfaren awem di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Lk. 24:47; Řex. 4:12; 13:38. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Ad awem dd-ariɣ, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* ibabaten\bd*, minzi aqa tessnem Wenni iǧan zeg umezwaru.  
\m Ad awem dd-ariɣ, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* ibřiɣen\bd*, minzi aqa tɣellbem x umɛeffan.  
\b  
\m Aqa uriɣ awem-dd, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* iḥudriyyen\bd*, minzi tessnem Babatneɣ.   
\m
\v 14 Aqa uriɣ awem-dd, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* ibabaten\bd*, minzi tessnem Wenni iǧan zeg umezwaru.  
\m Aqa uriɣ awem-dd, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* ibřiɣen\bd*, minzi aqa kenniw tjehdem uca Awař n AREBBI izeddeɣ daywem uca tɣellbem x umɛeffan.   
\b  
\m
\v 15 War ttexsem ca ddunect uřa d min iǧan di ddunect, minzi mařa ca n ijjen ittexs ddunect, tayri n Babatneɣ war dayes teǧi. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Gal. 1:10; Yaɛ. 4:4. \x*  
\v 16 Minzi marra min iǧan di ddunect - aqa-t d nnecwet n ddat d nnecwet n tiṭṭawin d tuffet n ddunect\add -a\add* - war dd-ittis ca zi Babatneɣ, maca zi ddunect.  
\v 17 Uca ddunect tɛeddu uřa d nnecwat nnes, maca wenni itteggen min ixs AREBBI, ad iqqim i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Izhd. 90:10; Ica. 40:6; 1 Kur. 7:31; Yaɛ. 1:10; 4:14; 1 Bṭ. 1:24. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lmasiḥ issxarriqen  
\m
\v 18 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* iḥenjiren inu\bd*, aqa řweqt taneggarut tiweḍ-dd, uca am tesřim belli ad dd-yas lmasiḥ afalsu, amenni řexxu ḍharen-dd aṭṭas n imasiḥen ifalsuten. S uyenni nessen belli řweqt taneggarut aqa tiweḍ-dd. \f ◼ \fr 2:18 \ft \+fk lmasiḥ afalsu\ft  - xzar 1 Yḥ. 2:18, 22; 4:3. Aqa din aṭṭas n iwdan inni iqqaren: ‘Lmasiḥ war iǧi d AREBBI! Netta d anabi!’ Man aya ixs ad yini belli nitni war ssteɛtarifen u war neɛɛmen ca, aqa AREBBI yusa-dd di arrimet n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ am mammec i d aneɣ isseřmed Wedlis Iqeddsen. S uyenni tteggen nitni am mammec ittegg lmasiḥ afalsu, war cehhden ca aqa Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ yusa-dd di arrimet. S uyenni ḍeffaren t deg ixarriqen nnes, nitni d iḥenjiren n ddejjař.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:18 \xt Mt. 24:5; 2 Ts. 2:3. \x*  
\v 19 Ffɣen-dd zzayneɣ, maca war ten tuɣi zzayneɣ. Meɛlik nitni tuɣa zzayneɣ, ad iři qqimen akidneɣ. Maca nitni ffɣen-dd zzayneɣ, ḥima ad iban belli nitni marra war ǧin ca zzayneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Izhd. 41:10; Řex. 20:30; 1 Kur. 11:19. \x*  
\v 20 Aqa ɣarwem adhan n Umqeddas uca tessnem ad tfarzem kuř ijj n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 2:20 \xt Izhd. 45:8; 133:2; 2 Kur. 1:21; Ɛbr. 1:9. \x*  
\v 21 War d awem uriɣ minzi war tessinem ca tidett, maca minzi aqa tᵉttessnem tt, u tessnem \add ɛawed\add* uřa d ijj n uxarriq war dd-itteffeɣ ca zi tidett.  
\v 22 Wi iǧan d bu-ixarriqen mɣir wenni inkaren belli Yasuɛ d Lmasiḥ! D wa d lmasiḥ afalsu, wenni inkaren Babas d Mmis. \f ◼ \fr 2:22 \ft \+fk lmasiḥ afalsu\ft  - xzar 1 Yḥ. 2:18 d 1 Yḥ. 4:3.\f*  
\v 23 Marra wenni inkaren Mmis war yumin ɛawed di Babas. Wenni icehhden i Mmis, icehhed ɛawed i Babas. \x ◘ \xo 2:23 \xt Lk. 12:9; 2 Tim. 2:12. \x*  
\v 24 Ejj ad daywem iqqim min tesřim zeg umezwaru. Mařa iqqim daywem min tesřim zeg umezwaru, ad teqqimem kenniw ɛawed di Babas u di Mmis.  
\v 25 Ta d tikkest n wawař i d aneɣ iwca: Tudart ittduman.   
\m
\v 26 Man aya uriɣ awem-t-i-dd x yinni kenniw ixeddɛen.  
\v 27 Mařa adhan i zzayes tᵉṭṭfem ad iqqim daywem, war teḥdajem ad kenniw isseřmed ḥed. Minzi adhan n AREBBI, ad kenniw isseřmad di marra, uca Netta d tidett war dayes ǧin ixarriqen. Xenni qqimem dayes, \add di Lmasiḥ\add*, am mammec i d awem isseřmed Netta. \x ◘ \xo 2:27 \xt Irm. 31:34; Ɛbr. 8:11. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 28 Xenni řexxu, \bd \+bdit a\+bdit* iḥenjiren inu\bd*, qqimem dayes, ḥima war nettseḍḥi ca qibač nnes x minni dd ɣa iḍhar, maca ad ɣarneɣ tiři ttiqqet ɣar twasit nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt Mk. 8:38; 1 Yḥ. 3:2. \x*  
\v 29 Mařa tessnem, belli Netta d amseggad, snem ɛawed belli marra wi itteggen tasegda, aqa \add ittwaxřeq-dd\add* zzayes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Tarwa n Arebbi  
\m
\v 1 Xzar, mecḥař temɣar tayri i zi d aneɣ ittexs Babatneɣ, ařami iřaɣa u igga aneɣ tarwa. S uyenni ddunect war d aneɣ tessin ca, minzi war t tessin ca. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Yḥ. 1:12. \x*  
\v 2 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* imɛizzen inu\bd*, řexxu neccin d tarwa n AREBBI i neǧa, war dd-iḍhar ɛad min ɣa niři. Aqa nessen xmi dd ɣa iban Netta, ad niři di ṣṣifet nnes, minzi ad t nẓar am mammec iǧa Netta. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Ica. 56:5; Mt. 5:12; Yḥ. 1:12; Rum. 8:15, 18; 2 Kur. 4:17; Gal. 3:26; 4:6; Fil. 3:21; Kul. 3:4. \x*  
\v 3 Marra wenni ɣar iǧa usitem-a dayes \add deg wuř nnes\add*, ad issizdeg ixef nnes, am mammec iǧa Netta d amezdag.  
\v 4 Marra wenni itteggen ddnub, ittegg řmuɛṣiyyet, minzi marra ddenb d řmuɛṣiyyet. \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Yḥ. 5:17. \x*  
\v 5 Tessnem belli Netta iban-dd, ḥima ad ikkes ddnub nneɣ: Netta war dayes bu ddnub. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Ica. 53:9, 12; 2 Kur. 5:21; 1 Bṭ. 2:22; 1 Tim. 1:15. \x*  
\v 6 Marra wi dayes i ɣa iqqimen, war ittegg ca ddnub. Marra wi itteggen ddnub, war t iẓri, war t issin.  
\v 7 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* iḥenjiren inu\bd*, war ttejjim ad kenniw ixarweḍ ḥed. Wenni itteggen tasegda d netta d amseggad am mammec ɛawed Lmasiḥ d amseggad. \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Yḥ. 2:29. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Wenni itteggen ddnub d netta zi cciṭan, minzi cciṭan tuɣa d amednub zeg umezwaru. I man aya i dd-iḍhar Mmis n AREBBI: ḥima ad issexsar řexdayem n cciṭan.   
\m
\v 9 Marra wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi AREBBI, war ittegg ca ddnub, minzi Zzariɛet nnes aqa-tt dayes uca war izemmar ad ixḍa, minzi ittwaxřeq-dd zi AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt 1 Bṭ. 1:23; 1 Yḥ. 5:18. \x*  
\v 10 Di man aya ad dd-ḍharen tarwa n AREBBI d tarwa n cciṭan: marra wenni war itteggen tasegda u war ittexsen umas, war iǧi ca zi AREBBI.  
\v 11 Maɣar ta d tawṣiyyet i tuɣa tesřim zeg umezwaru belli ad texsem ijjen wenneɣni!’ \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Yḥ. 13:34; 15:12; 1 Yḥ. 3:23. \x*  
\v 12 War iǧi am Qayin wenni iǧan zeg umɛeffan uca inɣa umas. Mayemmi inɣa umas? S minzi řexdayem nnes tuɣa atent ɛeffnent uca tinni n umas seggdent. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Amz. 4:8; 27:41; Ɛbr. 11:4. \x*  
\v 13 War tedhicem ca, \add a\add* aytma, mařa ddunect tcarh i kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Yḥ. 15:18. \x*  
\v 14 Neccin nessen, aqa neẓwa zi řmewt ɣar Tudart, minzi nexs awmaten nneɣ. Wenni war ittexsen umas, ad iqqim di řmewt. \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Yḥ. 2:10. \x*  
\v 15 Marra wi icarrhen umas d aqettař, uca kenniw tessnem belli Tudart ittduman war tzemmar ad teqqim deg ijj n uqettař. \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Mt. 5:21; Gal. 5:21. \x*  
\v 16 Zi man aya nessen tayri nnes i neccin, aqa Netta issars Tudart nnes deg wemcan nneɣ. Ɛawed ittxeṣṣa aneɣ nican ad nessars tudart nneɣ x aytmatneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt Yḥ. 15:13; Afa. 5:2. \x*  
\v 17 Wenni ɣar iǧa agřa n ddunect uca ittwařa umas izřeḍ, xenni iqqen xas uř nnes, mammec i ɣa tezdeɣ tayri n AREBBI dayes? \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt Aɛwd. 15:7; Lk. 3:11; Yaɛ. 2:15. \x*   
\m
\v 18 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* iḥenjiren inu\bd*, ejj aneɣ war nᵉttexs ijjen wenneɣni s wawař niɣ s iřes, maca s řexdayem u di tidett.  
\v 19 S man aya nessen aqa neccin zi tidett uca ad nesseqneɛ uřawen nneɣ qbeř i dd ɣa yas.  
\v 20 Minzi mařa iḥkem wuř nneɣ xaneɣ, mecḥař d ameqqran AREBBI x wuř nneɣ! Aqa Netta issen marra.  
\v 21 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* imɛizzen inu\bd*, mařa uř nneɣ war xaneɣ iḥkem, aqa ɣarneɣ ttiqqet zzat i AREBBI,  
\v 22 uca man řḥajjet i ɣa nettar, ad tt neksi zzayes, minzi neccin nḥeṭṭa tiweṣṣa nnes uca ad negg min ɣa yarḍan qibač Netta. \x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Irm. 29:12; Mt. 7:8; 21:22; Mk. 11:24; Lk. 11:9; Yḥ. 14:13; 16:24; Yaɛ. 1:5; 1 Yḥ. 5:14. \x*  
\v 23 D ta d tawṣeyyet nnes belli ad namen deg Yisem n Mmis Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ uca ad nexs ijj wenneɣni am mammec i d aneɣ yumur. \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt Lawi 19:18; Mt. 22:39; Yḥ. 6:29; 13:34, 35; 15:12; 17:3; Afa. 5:2; 1 Ts. 4:9; 1 Bṭ. 4:8; 1 Yḥ. 4:21. \x*  
\v 24 Wenni iḥeṭṭan tiweṣṣa nnes, ad zzayes ittwaḥḍa u Netta izeddeɣ dayes. S man aya nessen belli Netta ittɣima dayneɣ, zi Arruḥ nnes i d aneɣ iwca. \x ◘ \xo 3:24 \xt Yḥ. 14:23; 15:10; 1 Yḥ. 4:12. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Qeǧbem arruḥat  
\m
\v 1 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* imɛizzen inu\bd*, war ttiqqem ca di marra arruḥat, maca qeǧbem arruḥat, ma zi AREBBI i iǧan, minzi aṭṭas n inabiyyen issxarriqen aqa ffɣen-dd ɣar ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Irm. 29:8; Mt. 7:15, 16; 24:4, 5, 24; 1 Kur. 14:29; Afa. 5:6; Kul. 2:18; 2 Bṭ. 2:1; 2 Yḥ. 7. \x*  
\v 2 S man aya ad tessnem Arruḥ n AREBBI: marra arruḥ wenni icehhden belli Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ yusa-dd di ddat aqa netta zi AREBBI.  
\v 3 Marra arruḥ wenni war icehhden belli Yasuɛ yusa-dd di ddat, war iǧi ca zi AREBBI, maca zi arruḥ n lmasiḥ afalsu wenni i xef tesřam ad dd-yas, aqa netta da řexxu di ddunect. \f ◼ \fr 4:3 \ft \+fk lmasiḥ afalsu\ft  - xzar 1 Yḥ. 2:18, 22; 4:3. Aqa din aṭṭas n iwdan inni iqqaren: ‘Lmasiḥ war iǧi d AREBBI! Netta d anabi!’ Man aya ixs ad yini belli nitni war ssteɛtarifen u war neɛɛmen ca, aqa AREBBI yusa-dd di arrimet n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ am mammec i d aneɣ isseřmed Wedlis Iqeddsen. S uyenni tteggen nitni am mammec ittegg lmasiḥ afalsu, war cehhden ca aqa Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ yusa-dd di arrimet. S uyenni ḍeffaren t deg ixarriqen nnes, nitni d iḥenjiren n ddejjař.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt 2 Ts. 2:7; 1 Yḥ. 2:18, 22. \x*  
\v 4 Maca kenniw d tarwa n AREBBI i teǧam, aqa tɣellbem xasen, minzi d Wenni iǧan daywem d ameqqran x wenni iǧan di ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt 2 Ij. 6:16; 2 Im. 32:7; Yḥ. 16:33\x*  
\v 5 Nitni zi ddunect, s uyenni ssawařen zi ddunect uca ddunect tᵉttesřa asen-dd.  
\v 6 Aqa aneɣ zi AREBBI. Wenni issnen AREBBI, ittesřa aneɣ. Wenni war iǧin zi AREBBI war d aneɣ ittesři ca. S man aya i ɣa nessen Arruḥ n Tidett d arruḥ n uweddar. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Yḥ. 8:47; 10:27. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arebbi d Tayri  
\m
\v 7 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* imɛizzen inu\bd*, ejj aneɣ ad nexs ayawya, minzi tayri zi AREBBI, u marra wenni ittexsen, d netta ittwaxřeq-dd zi AREBBI uca issen AREBBI.  
\v 8 Minzi AREBBI d tayri, u wenni war ittexsen, war issin ca AREBBI.  
\v 9 S man aya teḍhar aneɣ-dd tayri n AREBBI, belli AREBBI aqa issekk-dd ayenni n Mmis i ɣares ɣar ddunect, ḥima ad zzayes neddar. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Yḥ. 3:16; Rum. 5:8. \x*  
\v 10 Di man aya i teǧa tayri, war iǧi belli neccin nᵉttexs AREBBI, maca belli Netta ittexs aneɣ uca issekk-dd Mmis d aṣřaḥ x ddnub nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt Rum. 3:24, 25; 2 Kur. 5:19; Kul. 1:19; 1 Yḥ. 2:2. \x*   
\m
\v 11 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* imɛizzen inu\bd*, mařa tuɣa AREBBI ittexs aneɣ ammu, ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ɛawed ad nexs ijj wenneɣni.  
\v 12 Uřa d ijjen ma iẓra AREBBI. Maca mařa nᵉttexs ayawya, AREBBI ad dayneɣ iqqim, uca tayri nnes aqa tedweř tekmeř dayneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Uf. 33:20; Aɛwd. 4:12; Yḥ. 1:18; 1 Tim. 1:17; 6:16; 1 Yḥ. 3:24. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Zi man aya nessen belli nettɣima dayes u Netta dayneɣ, minzi Netta iwca aneɣ zi Arruḥ nnes.  
\v 14 Aqa neẓra u ncehhed belli Babas issekk-dd Mmis d Amsenjem n ddunect.  
\v 15 Marra wenni icehhden belli Yasuɛ d Mmis n AREBBI, AREBBI ad dayes izdeɣ u netta ad izdeɣ di AREBBI.  
\v 16 Aqa neccin numen u nessen tayri tenni iǧan ɣar AREBBI i neccin. AREBBI d tayri u wenni i ɣa iqqimen di tayri, ad iqqim di AREBBI.   
\m
\v 17 Di man aya tᵉttwakemmeř tayri nnes dayneɣ, ařami ad ɣarneɣ tiři ttiqqet deg wass n lḥisab, minzi am mammec iǧa Netta, ad niři neccin ɛawed di ddunect-a.  
\v 18 Di tayri war tᵉttiři tiggʷudi, maca tayri nican tessuffuɣ tiggʷudi, minzi tiggʷudi tᵉttas-dd ak-d unexřiɛ. Wenni itteggʷeden, war ittiři ikmeř di tayri.  
\v 19 X uya ad nexs AREBBI, minzi Netta tuɣa ittexs aneɣ d amezwaru.  
\v 20 Mařa ca n ijjen iqqar: “Necc ttexseɣ AREBBI!”, am icarreh umas, aqa netta d bu-ixarriqen. Minzi wenni war ittexsen umas wenni ittwařa, xenni mammec ɣa yegg ad ixs AREBBI wenni war ittwiři. \x ◘ \xo 4:20 \xt 1 Yḥ. 2:4. \x*  
\v 21 Aqa tawṣeyyet-a neṭṭef i-tt zzayes, belli kuř ijjen i ittexsen AREBBI, ad ixs uřa d umas. \x ◘ \xo 4:21 \xt Lawi 19:18; Mt. 22:39; Yḥ. 13:34; 15:12; Afa. 5:2; 1 Ts. 4:9; 1 Bṭ. 4:8; 1 Yḥ. 3:23. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 L’iman di Mmis n Arebbi  
\m
\v 1 Marra wenni yumnen belli Yasuɛ d Lmasiḥ, aqa netta ittwaxřeq-dd zi AREBBI, uca marra wenni ittexsen wenni t-i-dd yejjin, ad ixs ɛawed wenni zzayes dd-ittwaxeřqen. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Yḥ. 1:12. \x*  
\v 2 Zi man aya nessen belli nᵉttexs tarwa n AREBBI, xmi nᵉttexs AREBBI u nᵉttegg tiweṣṣa nnes.  
\v 3 Minzi ta d tayri n AREBBI, ad neḥḍa tiweṣṣa nnes, uca tiweṣṣa nnes war wɛarent ca. \x ◘ \xo 5:3 \xt Mt. 11:29, 30; Yḥ. 14:15; 15:10. \x*  
\v 4 Maɣar mkuř ijjen i dd-ittwaxeřqen zi AREBBI ad iɣelleb x ddunect. D wa d aɣřab i ittɣellaben x ddunect, aqa-t d l’iman nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Yḥ. 16:33. \x*  
\v 5 Man wen i ɣa iɣellben x ddunect, mɣir wenni yumnen belli Yasuɛ d Mmis n AREBBI! \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt 1 Kur. 15:57; 1 Yḥ. 4:15. \x*  
\v 6 D Wa i dd-ikkin zeg waman d Idammen, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. War dd-yekki zeg waman waha, maca zeg waman d Idammen.  
\v 7 Arruḥ d wenni icehhden, minzi Arruḥ d tidett.  
\v 8 Aqa din třata n yinni icehhden: Arruḥ d waman d Idammen, uca nitni s třata deg ijjen.   
\m
\v 9 Mařa neqbeř cchadet n iwdan, mecḥař d tameqqrant cchadet n AREBBI. Ta d cchadet n AREBBI tenni iched x Mmis.  
\v 10 Wenni yumnen di Mmis n AREBBI, ɣares cchadet-a deg ixef nnes. Wenni war yuminen ca di AREBBI, aqa igga i-t d bu-ixarriqen, minzi netta war yumin ca di cchadet tenni iwca AREBBI x Mmis. \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Yḥ. 3:36; Rum. 8:16; Gal. 4:6. \x*  
\v 11 Uca ta d cchadet: AREBBI iwca aneɣ Tudart ittduman uca Tudart nni aqa-tt di Mmis. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Yḥ. 1:4. \x*  
\v 12 Wenni ɣar iǧa Mmis, ɣares Tudart. Wenni war ɣar iǧi Mmis n AREBBI, war ɣares bu Tudart.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Awař d useǧem ɣar uneggaru  
\m
\v 13 Uriɣ awem-dd man aya, ḥima ad tessnem belli ɣarwem Tudart ittduman, kenniw inni ittamnen deg Yisem n Mmis n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt Yḥ. 20:31. \x*   
\m
\v 14 D ta d ttiqqet tenni ɣarneɣ dayes, mařa nettar zzayes ca n řḥajjet ɛlaḥsab min ixs Netta, Netta ad ɣarneɣ iseř. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Irm. 29:12; Mt. 7:8; 21:22; Mk. 11:24; Lk. 11:9; Yḥ. 14:13; 15:7; 16:24; Yaɛ. 1:5; 1 Yḥ. 3:2. \x*  
\v 15 Mařa nettwasseqneɛ nican aqa ad aneɣ iseř min ma d as nettar, xenni nettiqq belli aqa yusa-dd aneɣ min d as nettar.   
\m
\v 16 Mařa ḥed iẓra umas ixeṭṭa, ijj n uxeṭṭu war ihdijen ca řmewt, ejj i-t ad iẓẓaǧ \add di ṭṭweɛ nnes\add*, uca ad as temmewc Tudart, i wenni war ixeṭṭin ca ař řmewt. Aqa din axeṭṭu ař řmewt, war qqareɣ ca aqa ittxeṣṣa ad iẓẓaǧ i man aya. \x ◘ \xo 5:16 \xt Řxř. 15:30; 1 Ṣm. 2:25; Mt. 12:31; Mk. 3:29; Lk. 12:10; Ɛbr. 6:4; 10:26; 2 Bṭ. 2:2. \x*  
\v 17 Marra řmuɛṣiyyet, aqa-tt d ddenb uca aqa din ddenb i war iǧin ca ař řmewt. \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt 1 Yḥ. 3:4. \x*   
\m
\v 18 Nessen belli kuř ijjen wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi AREBBI, war ixeṭṭi ca, minzi wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi AREBBI ad iḥḍa ixef nnes u amɛeffan war t ittḥidi.\x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt 1 Yḥ. 3:9. \x*  
\v 19 Nessen, aqa aneɣ zi AREBBI uca ddunect marra aqa-tt deg \add ifassen n\add* umɛeffan.  
\v 20 Nessen belli Mmis n AREBBI aqa yusa-dd uca iwca aneɣ-dd řefhamet ḥima ad nessen Wenni iǧan d tidett u ḥima ad niři deg Wenni d tidett, di Mmis Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. D wa d AREBBI s tidett d Tudart ittduman. \x ◘ \xo 5:20 \xt Ica. 9:5; 44:6; 53:11; 54:5; Lk. 24:45; Yḥ. 20:28; Rum. 9:5; 1 Tim. 3:16. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 21 \bd \+bdit A\+bdit* iḥenjiren inu\bd*, ḥḍam ixef nwem zeg weɛbed n l’aṣnam!   